<br>
It was doable but I found myself FD' binding up to attack again almost every time I didn't have mend ready.<br>
<br>
Do you have any aa points in first aid?  I think that would have made a big difference to me but I am not certain.<br>
<br>
Also I didn't figure out the ID trick untill I was level 60.  If your ID skill is maxed it should help you a little if you pull everything up past the second ladder.  <br>
<br>
Another bit of advice.  If you are pulling wolves up to the second ladder they won't be able to climb the ladders like the spiders and bears do.  Instead you will have to have them warp on you.  I think the way I would do this is to run up both ladders and stand just out of reach of the second ladder.  If you stand within reach the dog will end up running the wrong way.  If you stay just out of reach they will warp on you.<br>
